\par   * There is now a preferences window which allows for changing of colors on the map display, font sizes, and more.
\par   * Your own unit is now drawn in a bold line on the tactical map to help differentiate it in large battles.
\par   * You can now show cliffs, which will highlight edges in red which will cause a fall or halt.
\par   * Changes to internal way that maps are stored.
\par   * Thud will now exit when the main window is closed.
\par   
\par  }{\i\f38\insrsid2255033 Bug Fixes:}{\f4\insrsid2255033 
\par   
\par   * Thud now handles underground maps properly (unknown hexes show up black on the tactical display).
\par   * Some work on map correctness done, but there's still more to do.
