\par }{\i\f38\insrsid2255033  New Features:}{\f4\insrsid2255033 
\par 
\par   * The map can now be scrolled around the main unit. The commands are in the 'Map' menu, and are most effective when using the keyboard shortcuts.
\par   * Weapons arcs can now reflect the range of your weapons in that particular arc or 1 hex (whichever is longer). For exampl
